card.description: ERIC is a non-profit organization whose mission is to assist states in improving the accuracy of America’s voter rolls. ERIC is governed and managed by states who choose to join, and was formed in 2012 with assistance from The Pew Charitable Trusts. Feel free to get in touch with us for more info!
card.title: Improving Voter Registration For Member States
